---
/**
 * Canonical RFF brand lockup - mirrors `RFFAppLockup` in the platform's
 * `Brand.tsx` so the marketing site and the platform read as the same product.
 *
 * Mark: double-chevron (forward-slashes / fast-forward), second chevron at
 * 60% opacity for motion. Sits on a violet rounded-square fill.
 * Wordmark: lowercase `rff`, italicized trailing `f`, Inter Tight 800.
 *
 * If we ever want the full lockup with the "Really Freakin' Fast" tagline
 * (e.g. on the footer or login screen), port `RFFWordmark` from Brand.tsx
 * the same way - same SVG, just stack the tagline below in JetBrains Mono.
 */
---
<a href="/" aria-label="RFF home" class="rff-logo">
  <span class="mark" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">
      <path d="M 8 24 L 16 8" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" />
      <path d="M 16 24 L 24 8" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6" />
    </svg>
  </span>
  <span class="word">rf<span class="word-italic">f</span></span>
</a>

<style>
  .rff-logo {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .mark {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;          /* round(28 * 0.28) - matches Brand.tsx */
    background: var(--brand);    /* violet, same token as the platform */
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .word {
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .word-italic {
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
